tool_description: This API uses the birth as well as progressed astrological charts of people to determine their basic as well as current compatibility.

api_list.name: match
api_list.description: Accepts a string parameter containing the first person's name and birth date, followed by up to 10 other people and their birth dates to apply the astrological matching algorithms and return them in order of most to least compatible.

required_parameters.name: birthdetails
required_parameters.description: A string containing names and birth dates of individuals for compatibility analysis.
required_parameters.default: name=Jennifer Aniston&dob=2/11/1969&name1=Justin Theroux&dob1=8/10/1971&name2=Gerard Butler&dob2=11/13/1969&name3=John Mayer&dob3=10/16/1977&name4=Paul Sculfor&dob4=2/1/1971&name5=David Schwimmer&dob5=11/2/1969&name6=Vince Vaughn&dob6=3/28/1970&name7=Brad Pitt&dob7=12/18/1963&name8=Paul Rudd&dob8=4/6/1969&name9=Tate Donovan&dob9=9/25/1963&name10=Daniel McDonald&dob10=7/30/1960&sort=S&NC=C&ryr=2023&details=N&coupon=12345678

optional_parameters.name: birthdetails
optional_parameters.description: An optional string for additional birth details.
